Package: ESPI
Title: Single-Cell Analysis of E-Stim in p27CKO Retina
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Megan", "Stone", , "megan.stone@vanderbilt.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Carl", "Stone", , "carl.j.stone@vanderbilt.edu", role = "aut")
    )
Description: Reproducible single-cell RNA-sequencing analysis comparing p27CKO
    mouse retina with and without E-Stim. Provides package
    helpers and executable scripts for count processing, quality control,
    clustering, Müller glia selection, pseudobulk differential analysis, and
    manuscript figures.
